For order no:
--------------
- SE11
- select domain- ZONO_28 
- short descp - Order number
- Data type  NUMC
- No of character 10
- click enter
- ctrl +s for save, ctl+f2 for sytax check and ctl+f3 for activation
 
  
For order date:
--------------
- SE11
- select domain- ZODATE_28 
- short descp - Order DATE
- Data type  DATC
- No of character 8
- click enter
- ctrl +s for save, ctl+f2 for sytax check and ctl+f3 for activation

For Payment mode:
--------------
- SE11
- select domain- ZPM_28 
- short descp - Payment Mode
- Data type  CHARS
- No of character 1
- click on value range
 Fixed    short descript
   C        Credit card
   D        Debit card
   n         netbanknig

- click enter
- ctrl +s for save, ctl+f2 for sytax check and ctl+f3 for activation


For Total amount:
------------------
- SE11
- select domain- ZTC 
- short descp - Total amount
- Data type  CURRY
- No of character 7
- Decimal places 2
- click enter
- ctrl +s for save, ctl+f2 for sytax check and ctl+f3 for activation

For Total amount:
------------------
- SE11
- select domain- ZCUR_28
- short descp - CURRENCY
- Data type  CUKY
- No of character 5
- click enter
- ctrl +s for save, ctl+f2 for sytax check and ctl+f3 for activation


